<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
        h1 { color: #2c3e50; border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        h2 { color: #2980b9; margin-top: 30px; }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        th, td { padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: left; }
        th { background-color: #f8f9fa; color: #2c3e50; }
        .buy { color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold; } /* US: Green for Buy */
        .sell { color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold; } /* US: Red for Sell */
        .positive { color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold; }
        .negative { color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold; }
        .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d; margin-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Squeeze Analysis - Daily Summary (US) v{{ app_version }}</h1>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{ date }}</p>

        <h2>Strategy Notes</h2>
        <p><strong>Houyi</strong>: strong stocks pulling back into key zones, looking for a renewed move.</p>
        <p><strong>Whale</strong>: daily and weekly momentum turning up together, better for swing-style setups.</p>

        {% if priority_count > 0 %}
        <h2>⭐ Priority Watchlist (Top 10)</h2>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ticker</th>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <th>Signal</th>
                    <th>Houyi</th>
                    <th>Whale</th>
                    <th>Priority Score</th>
                    <th>Momentum</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {% for item in priority_results %}
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>{{ item.ticker }}</strong></td>
                    <td>{{ item.name }}</td>
                    <td class="buy">{{ item.signal }}</td>
                    <td>{{ 'Yes' if item.has_houyi else 'No' }}</td>
                    <td>{{ 'Yes' if item.has_whale else 'No' }}</td>
                    <td>{{ item.composite_score }}</td>
                    <td>{{ "%.4f"|format(item.momentum) if item.momentum else 'N/A' }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <p>Base buy/watch list: {{ buy_count }} | Houyi matches: {{ houyi_count }} | Whale matches: {{ whale_count }}</p>
        {% else %}
        <h2>No Priority Watchlist Today</h2>
        <p>No stocks cleared a strong enough mix of signal strength and Houyi/Whale priority factors.</p>
        <p>Base buy/watch list: {{ buy_count }} | Houyi matches: {{ houyi_count }} | Whale matches: {{ whale_count }}</p>
        {% endif %}

        {% if sell_count > 0 %}
        <h2>⚠️ Sell Recommendations (Top 10)</h2>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Ticker</th>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <th>Signal</th>
                    <th>Momentum</th>
                    <th>Energy</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {% for item in sell_results %}
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>{{ item.ticker }}</strong></td>
                    <td>{{ item.name }}</td>
                    <td class="sell">{{ item.signal }}</td>
                    <td>{{ "%.4f"|format(item.momentum) if item.momentum else 'N/A' }}</td>
                    <td>{{ "%.1f"|format(item.energy) }}</td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        {% endif %}

        {% if tracking_buys %}
        <h2>📈 Performance Tracking (Buy)</h2>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Latest Entry</th>
                    <th>Entries</th>
                    <th>Ticker</th>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <th>Avg Entry Price</th>
                    <th>Current Price</th>
                    <th>Days</th>
                    <th>Return (%)</th>
                    <th>Stop Alert</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {% for perf in tracking_buys %}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{ perf.latest_entry_date }}</td>
                    <td>{{ perf.entries }}</td>
                    <td><strong>{{ perf.ticker }}</strong></td>
                    <td>{{ perf.name }}</td>
                    <td>${{ "%.2f"|format(perf.avg_entry_price) }}</td>
                    <td>${{ "%.2f"|format(perf.current_price) }}</td>
                    <td>{{ perf.days_tracked }}</td>
                    <td class="{{ 'positive' if perf.return_pct > 0 else 'negative' }}">
                        {{ "%.2f"|format(perf.return_pct) }}%
                    </td>
                    <td class="{{ 'negative' if perf.stop_loss_triggered else '' }}">
                        {{ perf.stop_loss_message if perf.stop_loss_message else '-' }}
                    </td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="footer">
            *Generated by Squeeze Stock Screener. Charts for Top picks are attached.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
